text: Desmiphora magnifica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1995. It is known from Brazil and French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora magnifica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1995
